{"tid":472510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[紀錄片]香港地鐵紀錄片（建造史）","createTime":"2017-11-18T10:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T00:01:33.000Z","uid":41818,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"04596f3f711706ac68c31b57f33a045e67823f25","tid":472510,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"&quot;Underground Iron - The Building of a Railway&quot; was a documentary of Hong Kong Mass Transit Railway Corporation (MTRC), reviewing the building background, process and benefit of the initial system of MTR. This original documentary was released in 1986, the time frame was longer than Cantonese version which played on TV channels. <br />\n<br />\n<ins><em><strong>《地鐵》- 香港地鐵興建工程是一輯由香港地下鐵路公司拍攝的紀錄片，介紹當年香港地鐵的興建原因、過程和對香港的得益。此片在 1986 年製作成錄影帶，屬英文原版，比當年電視播放的時間較長。</strong></em></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPart 1: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/B-q0laX4nYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB-q0laX4nYA&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=bb54d922\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B-q0laX4nYA</a><br />\nPart 2: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fiC4iX0D27c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfiC4iX0D27c&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ce0525df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fiC4iX0D27c</a><br />\nPart 3: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/ru9uMkxmGyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fru9uMkxmGyc&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a60a3458\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ru9uMkxmGyc</a><br />\nPart 4: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/UjwiScZkZAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUjwiScZkZAw&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=febaceef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UjwiScZkZAw</a><br />\nPart 5: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/bfSZJtLkukU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbfSZJtLkukU&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1d187911\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bfSZJtLkukU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地鐵紀錄片，睇完先知道當年地鐵嘅興建難度原來咁大"},{"pid":"4e50e122c55a75e0818169a8c409d6b82f0ac061","tid":472510,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"呢套好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab21cc6ceb9a9485bfbb3f885dd623da5d0fb72b","tid":472510,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"好睇"},{"pid":"c6fb8071608ba7662afacb0a47e740a470d3e107","tid":472510,"uid":28195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"高鐵敢唔敢拍返套？"},{"pid":"61eb4a787d420bf5a8c463c9bd50a29a720b4245","tid":472510,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係old news啱啱先發現到呢套紀錄片 <br />\nd backgroud music好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dce6aae6b87ff5566b7dcd53c6c0bcb3f530b19","tid":472510,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高鐵敢唔敢拍返套？</blockquote><br />\n如果高鐵應該仲難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過同地鐵可比既應該用沙中線好啲"},{"pid":"5cd8dc3fed0a6efa45fad18a98abe8e810504ab6","tid":472510,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高鐵敢唔敢拍返套？</blockquote><br />\n如果高鐵應該仲難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過同地鐵可比既應該用沙中線好啲</blockquote><br />\n高鐵有咩好拍"},{"pid":"db26d02c5b7b03f3d2a2455c8ae7cad7d46ded22","tid":472510,"uid":52737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"894f553cc5b386f9e59e015e6f9866ac82d51d36","