左西九高鐵？</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"a5176697523c5addc86a37ecdc4414c30f3ab02d","tid":472510,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc09db41fee7995e71e0138d3200790bcc5709f","tid":472510,"uid":45358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"Good post LM"},{"pid":"2e5af7d202b9e7e67a9104c954348f16e0c795c9","tid":472510,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"聽老豆講<br />\n起港島線搞到間日本公司要破產？"},{"pid":"8b82b82648e181f3bd3dab149b5751266b42df76","tid":472510,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>片入面見到港島線，有唔少係日本公司參與興建</blockquote><br />\n係 見到慶祝係飲清酒</blockquote><br />\n所以地鐵硬件係超班，不過到依家既管理已經跌返落average既水平</blockquote><br />\n黃種人就係爭D</blockquote><br />\n正話睇曬, 入面影到嘅華人工程師少之又少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得make sense ，大英既tube 同鐵路系統有成百年歷史，又經歷過二次大戰，只講實戰經驗的話，俾佢地lead係好正常，香港既engineer可以係側邊學野偷師（見過唔少英國佬係肯教野既），已經終生受用。<br />\n<br />\n另外搵日本仔做，當年英國佬好明顯係有思考過，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為60年代日本JR鐵路系統已經係好先進同嚴緊</span>，亞洲肯定第一，有遠東業界龍頭幫手，所以香港地鐵既foundation係超哂班</blockquote> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底知唔知自己噏乜? <br />\nMTRC關營團同東京都交通局咩事? JNR嗰陣先做完通勤五方面作戰 <br />\nMTR工程日本contactor係自身經濟黃金時期, 地下結構同隧道建築技術同經驗夠, 特別熊谷組泡沫未爆前靠海外project做到當地五大入面最大"},{"pid":"6260ba269470c646b1858243d717158376c5cf63","tid":472510,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T01:46:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"cdcc7db